     <h1>
      YOUR LETTERS AND COMMENTS
     </h1>
     <h1>
      This page is dedicated to all those that want the Oceanway to proceed and why we think it should happen. We'll put comments up here that have been written on the petition, that people send through to us and from the letters to the Gold Coast Sun's editor. Let's tell  everyone that visits this page, why the beachside Oceanway is important to us!
     </h1>
     <a href="contact.html">
      Please Use the Form on Contact Page to send in your comments
      <br />
      <br />
